1.4.20  9:55 am   Wtf should I do when I get an anxiety attack? I get them more and more often.
I have tried: breathing slowly, calling my mum/dad or a friend, watching a video to distract myself, and pacing around. Nothing works because there's this overwhelming, cold, all-consuming tide of pressure and terror rising up inside me while my brain is trying SO hard to fight it and I just end up hyperventilating and sobbing. There has to be a better way to deal with it.
